## Install

- Install Go
- Install [dep](https://golang.github.io/dep/docs/installation.html)

```
$ brew install goreleaser
$ brew install dep
```

## Get Source

```
$ go get bitbucket.org/auzty/gobackup
$ cd $GOPATH/src/bitbucket.org/auzty/gobackup/
$ dep ensure
```

## Test

```
$ make test
```

## Release new version

```
$ git tag 0.7.3
$ make release
```
